import { Container, Row, Col } from 'react-bootstrap'
import Header from './Header'
import PushOffCanvas from './PushOffCanvas'
import '../styles/Home.css'

export default function Home(){

    return (
        <>
            <PushOffCanvas />

            <main className="pushcanvas-content main my-6">
                <Header />
                <section className="carousel my-1">
                </section>

                <section className="nav-cards p-1 p-md-3">
                    <Container>
                        <Row className="gap-2">
                            <Col>
                            
                            </Col>

                            <Col>
                            </Col>

                            <Col>
                            </Col>
                        </Row>
                    </Container>
                </section>

                <section className="products">
                    <Container></Container>
                </section>
            </main>

        </>
    )
}
